message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper proposes a method for automatic estimation of fetal abdominal circumference from ultrasound images using a specially designed convolutional neural network (CNN). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses Hough transformation, which is a classic computer vision technique, and the proposed CNN takes into account doctors' decision process and anatomical structure, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper is focused on medical imaging and diagnosis, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.MED (Medical Imaging) and cs.NEURON (Neurons and Cognition).
